STATE
v.
Keyshawn JONES. No. 27P16-1. Supreme Court of North Carolina. Jan. 26, 2016. John F. Carella, Assistant Appellate Defender, for Jones, Keyshawn. Rajeev K. Premakumar, Assistant Attorney General, for State of North Carolina. Robert C. Montgomery, Special Deputy Attorney General, for State of North Carolina. Matthew Delbridge, District Attorney, for State of North Carolina.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 25th of January 2016 by State of NC for Temporary Stay:

"Motion Allowed by order of the Court in conference, this the 26th of January 2016."
